  "text": "Oncotarget 2013; 4: 584-599 586 www.impactjournals.com/oncotarget glucose uptake rate and decreased O 2 consumption in thyroid cancer cells [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . However, no evidence exists that V600E BRAF regulates the expression of individual glycolytic enzymes, as seen with RAS and MYC. Also, potential bioenergetic factors responsible for the addiction of melanoma cells to V600E BRAF remain unaddressed.",
